---
Author: Lao Tzu
Source:
  - Title: Tao Te Ching
    Chapter: 53
Tags:
  - separation
  - path
---
If I only had the tiniest grain of wisdom,
    I would walk in the great way,
and my only fear would be to stray from it.

The great way is smooth and straight
    and yet the people prefer the difficult paths.
